@startuml Integration Sequence Diagram
!theme plain

title Enterprise HSE Platform — Integration Sequence Diagram

actor "User" as user
participant "FastAPI\nBackend" as api
participant "Integration\nLayer" as integration
participant "SAP ERP" as sap
participant "HRIS" as hris
participant "SCADA\n(OPC-UA)" as scada
participant "IoT Gateway\n(MQTT)" as iot
participant "Email\nGateway" as email
participant "SMS\nGateway" as sms
participant "Power BI" as powerbi
participant "Grafana" as grafana
participant "PostgreSQL\nEDW" as pg

' SAP Integration Flow
user -> api : Update equipment master data
api -> integration : Route to SAP connector
integration -> sap : PUT /Equipment/{id}\n(OData)
sap --> integration : 200 OK\nUpdated ETag
integration --> api : Success response
api --> user : Equipment updated

' HRIS Daily Sync
user -> api : Trigger HR sync (scheduled)
api -> integration : Route to HRIS connector
integration -> hris : GET /Employees\n(LDAP/REST)
hris --> integration : 200 OK\nEmployee list
integration -> pg : UPSERT dim_employee\n(upsert logic)
pg --> integration : Success
integration --> api : Sync complete\n(150 employees)
api --> user : HR sync completed

' SCADA Real-time Data
scada -> iot : Sensor reading\n(PM2.5: 35 µg/m³)
iot -> integration : Publish MQTT\nTopic: hse/env/SITE-A
integration -> api : Webhook/POST\n/api/v1/integrations/scada
api -> pg : INSERT environmental_reading\n(validated)
pg --> api : Success
api -> integration : Trigger alert evaluation
integration -> email : Send alert email\n(to: hse.officer@company.com)
email --> integration : 250 OK\nAccepted
integration --> api : Alert sent
api --> user : Display alert on dashboard

' Power BI Export
user -> api : Request data export\n(for Power BI)
api -> integration : Route to Power BI connector
integration -> powerbi : POST /datasets/{id}/rows\n(REST/ODBC)
powerbi --> integration : 200 OK\nRows ingested
integration --> api : Export complete\n(1000 rows)
api --> user : Export successful

' Grafana Real-time Metrics
user -> api : Request dashboard metrics
api -> integration : Publish to Grafana
integration -> grafana : POST /api/dashboards/db\n(JSON payload)
grafana --> integration : 200 OK\nDashboard updated
integration --> api : Metrics published
api --> user : Display dashboard

' SMS Alert Flow
user -> api : Acknowledge alert
api -> integration : Trigger SMS notification
integration -> sms : POST /messages\n(REST API)
sms --> integration : 200 OK\nMessage ID: 12345
integration --> api : Notification sent
api --> user : Alert acknowledged\n(SMS sent to PIC)

@enduml
